        <title>工作、消费主义和新穷人</title>
        <link>https://kanrw.github.io/p/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B0%E7%A9%B7%E4%BA%BA/</link>
